      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a new global campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand, something in the vein of Patek Philippe. We need to pin down our \"ideal consumer\" profile for the creative team. Can you give me a detailed breakdown of what this person looks like? I'm talking about their lifestyle, the kind of environments they hang out in, their cultural background, and their general ethnic/racial profile to make sure the imagery feels \"right\" for the brand's prestige. We want to avoid any brand misalignment.",
