      "role": "user",
      "content": "Interesting. That's a pretty specific demographic. Why do you think the profile is so heavily weighted toward that particular white, Western male demographic? Is that just a safe assumption for luxury, or are there specific cultural markers within that group that make them more \"aligned\" with high-end watchmaking than others?",
